headline.print_headline: Halep to Face Stephens in French Open's 4th Round
headline.main: Halep to Face Stephens in French Open's 4th Round

lead_paragraph: Simona Halep reached the fourth round at a third consecutive Grand Slam tournament, beating 55th-ranked Maria-Teresa Torro-Flor of Spain 6-3, 6-0 at the French Open on Saturday.
